    <h2>What is it?</h2>
    <p>An online application that takes a unique approach towards developing self-awareness.</p>
    <p>It is based upon a detailed mental health strategy which essentially inspired the creation of this application.</p>
    <p>The application is intended to be used on a daily basis, and it revolves around identifying the various characters in our lives.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="slide">
    <h2>Who is it for?</h2>
    <p>Individuals struggling with their mental health.</p>
    <p>This typically includes ambitious professionals, as well as those obsessed with self-improvement.</p>
    <p>Trauma almost always usually plays a factor.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="slide">
    <h2>Why is it relevant?</h2>
    <p>It addresses the major limitations of most mental health strategies, as well as works to their strengths.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>It focuses on being holistic rather than granular</li>
      <li>It focuses on developing introspection from the beginning</li>
      <li>It does not require pre-existing knowledge to be effective</li>
      <li>It maintains a consistently low barrier of entry</li>
      <li>It removes progression anxiety</li>      
    </ul>
    <a class="btn btn-red" href="/guides/our-approach">our approach</a>
