  <div class="slide">
    <h2>How does it work?</h2>
    <p>This strategy revolves around these things I call 'characters'.</p>
    <p>Characters are the various personalities we play when we're angry, sad, irrational and everything else in-between.</p>
    <p>The aim is to identify these characters and ultimately dissolve them.</p>
    <p>Why? a) Because these characters are not real.</p>


